{"tid":2062471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其搞BLM遊行，我覺得應該搞支持南亞慘死手足，主題為all lives matter +反警暴","createTime":"2020-06-13T07:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T07:32:04.000Z","uid":31215,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d55fb4539193a671fdf5ad1c35075d67ba36df32","tid":2062471,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"佢地自己搞得咁少人去<br />\n<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/05-18-2020/t_f75c23d5735643a7abdf774c6e55c982_name_1589785686_7bf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F05-18-2020%2Ft_f75c23d5735643a7abdf774c6e55c982_name_1589785686_7bf2.jpg&h=26e2b232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺同一個地方，受同一種警暴<br />\n我地應該將blm浪潮本土化<br />\n喺尖沙咀搞<br />\n支持南亞手足，歡迎南亞朋友參與，唔落得場都喺重慶大廈睇下我地<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想香港展示到包容文化<br />\n今次遊行值得搞<br />\n同埋呢單野真係不公不義<br />\n<br />\n連登仔點睇<br />\n認同請幫推<br />\n我地坐言起行搵一個星期六日做左佢<br />\n<br />\n示威前後仲可以幫襯重慶<br />\n收到風有啲鋪撐得好辛苦"},{"pid":"8831f2d2dbdf5b2e3a99a78ca60a967375985c60","tid":2062471,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"一個醉酒佬俾警犬殺死<br />\n無啦啦又變咗你手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0277885fdb38c9f4830b65481fff48d7d29d7692","tid":2062471,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8831f2d2dbdf5b2e3a99a78ca60a967375985c60","tid":2062471,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"一個醉酒佬俾警犬殺死<br />\n無啦啦又變咗你手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"打錯標題<br />\n係嗰個南亞人<br />\n唔係手足<br />\n<br />\n美國blm死嗰個都係罪犯<br />\n就算當事人有問題<br />\n唔代表可以咁樣俾人殺死"},{"pid":"95154eaddbf217e64bb291481157f0689f358cb4","tid":2062471,"uid":200083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"搞你老母咩 好撚得閒啊？"},{"pid":"4a03b8485cf65fb166c8a0b2c7b43